\f0\b\fs48 \cf4 \cb3 The Kidney 
\f1\b0\fs36 \cf2 \cb1 \
\pard\tx560\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Humans have two kidneys. Each kidney consists of a 
\f0\b cortex 
\f1\b0 (outer portion where blood enters the kidney), a 
\f0\b medulla 
\f1\b0 (middle portion), and a 
\f0\b pelvis 
